<div class="cap-check">✓ INCLUDED</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class="section-divider"></div>

<!-- ── DETECTION PATTERNS (NEW) ── -->
<section id="detection">
<div class="container">
<div class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="det_label">Detection Engine</div>
<div class="section-title reveal" data-i18n="det_title">What We Detect.</div>
<div class="section-sub reveal" data-i18n="det_sub">23+ detection patterns across financial crime and card fraud — each powered by rule engines, ML models, and graph analytics.</div>

<div class="detect-category reveal">
<h3><span class="cat-icon">🔍</span> <span data-i18n="det_cat1">Financial Crime Patterns</span> <span class="cat-count">16</span></h3>
<div class="detect-grid">
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">💰</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp1_t">Structuring / Smurfing</h4><p data-i18n="dp1_d">Splitting transactions below reporting thresholds (e.g. $9,900 each)</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">📊</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp2_t">Layering</h4><p data-i18n="dp2_d">Multi-layered transfer chains to obscure fund origins</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🔄</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp3_t">Round-Tripping</h4><p data-i18n="dp3_d">Funds returning to origin through different paths</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">📤</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp4_t">Fan-Out (1→N)</h4><p data-i18n="dp4_d">One account distributing to many recipients</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">📥</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp5_t">Fan-In (N→1)</h4><p data-i18n="dp5_d">Many accounts collecting into a single destination</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🔀</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp6_t">Fan-In/Out Combo</h4><p data-i18n="dp6_d">Collection + distribution combination (mixer pattern)</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🫏</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp7_t">Muling</h4><p data-i18n="dp7_d">Recruited money mule accounts used as intermediaries</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🧾</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp8_t">Invoice Fraud (Naylon Fatura)</h4><p data-i18n="dp8_d">Fictitious invoices creating legitimate-looking transfers</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🚢</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp9_t">Trade-Based Laundering</h4><p data-i18n="dp9_d">Over/under invoicing, phantom shipments, and fictitious goods</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🏢</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp10_t">Shell Company Networks</h4><p data-i18n="dp10_d">Front company networks used to obscure fund flows</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">⏱️</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp11_t">Funnel Accounts</h4><p data-i18n="dp11_d">Accounts opened, heavily used, and quickly abandoned</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">⚡</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp12_t">Rapid Movement</h4><p data-i18n="dp12_d">Funds transferred out within minutes of deposit</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">💤</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp13_t">Dormant Activation</h4><p data-i18n="dp13_d">Long-inactive accounts suddenly becoming active</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">💱</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp14_t">Currency Cycling</h4><p data-i18n="dp14_d">Circular conversion between different currencies</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">₿</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp15_t">Crypto Mixing</h4><p data-i18n="dp15_d">Mixer/tumbler services used for crypto laundering</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🪆</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="dp16_t">Nested Services</h4><p data-i18n="dp16_d">Fintech operating through another fintech (Matryoshka pattern)</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="detect-category reveal">
<h3><span class="cat-icon">💳</span> <span data-i18n="det_cat2">Card Fraud Patterns</span> <span class="cat-count">7</span></h3>
<div class="detect-grid">
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🏪</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf1_t">MCC Analysis</h4><p data-i18n="cf1_d">Merchant Category Code anomalies and high-risk MCC monitoring</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">↩️</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf2_t">Chargeback Fraud</h4><p data-i18n="cf2_d">Systematic chargeback abuse and friendly fraud patterns</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🌐</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf3_t">CNP Fraud</h4><p data-i18n="cf3_d">Card-not-present transaction fraud and velocity anomalies</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">📋</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf4_t">Card Cloning</h4><p data-i18n="cf4_d">Duplicate card usage detection across locations and devices</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">⚠️</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf5_t">Merchant Risk</h4><p data-i18n="cf5_d">High-risk merchant scoring and transaction laundering detection</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🔓</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf6_t">3D Secure Bypass</h4><p data-i18n="cf6_d">Attempts to circumvent 3DS authentication protocols</p></div></div>
<div class="detect-card"><div class="d-icon">🔢</div><div class="d-info"><h4 data-i18n="cf7_t">BIN Analysis</h4><p data-i18n="cf7_d">Bank Identification Number pattern analysis and anomaly detection</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class="section-divider"></div>

<section id="solutions">
<div class="container">
<div class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="sol_label">Solutions</div>
