<div class="sector-panel active" id="sector-banks">
<h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px">🏦 Banks & Financial Institutions</h3>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:24px">Purpose-built feature set for banks & financial institutions.</p>
<div class="sector-features"><div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Transaction Monitoring</h4><p>Real-time and batch screening of wire transfers, card payments, ATM, and POS transactions.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>SAR/STR Filing</h4><p>Auto-generated suspicious activity reports with maker-checker approval and direct regulatory submission.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Customer Risk Scoring</h4><p>Continuous KYC risk assessment across behavioral, transactional, and network dimensions.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Case Management</h4><p>Full investigation lifecycle — alert triage, evidence collection, graph exploration, disposition tracking.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Graph Visualization</h4><p>Interactive money flow maps with timeline playback, Sankey diagrams, and collaborative analysis.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Credit Card Fraud</h4><p>MCC analysis, chargeback patterns, CNP fraud, card cloning detection, merchant risk scoring.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Decision Engine</h4><p>Auto-approve, auto-block, or route to review based on risk score. Dynamic transaction limits.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Regulatory Compliance</h4><p>FinCEN, MASAK, NCA, AMLD6 — country-specific formatting and filing protocols.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sector-panel" id="sector-fiu">
<h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px">🏛️ Financial Intelligence Units</h3>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:24px">Purpose-built feature set for financial intelligence units.</p>
<div class="sector-features"><div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Cross-Institutional Analysis</h4><p>Analyze fund flows across multiple banks and financial institutions simultaneously.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Network Intelligence</h4><p>Detect criminal organizations through graph analysis of cross-border transaction patterns.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Regulatory Reporting</h4><p>goAML integration, FATF typology mapping, and country-specific STR/CTR generation.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Investigation Toolkit</h4><p>Entity 360° view, pivot analysis, what-if scenarios, and historical playback.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>War Room Mode</h4><p>Multi-analyst collaborative investigation with shared graph workspace and real-time annotation.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Forensic Replay</h4><p>Re-run any historical transaction against the rules and models active at that time.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sector-panel" id="sector-fintech">
<h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px">💳 Fintechs & Neobanks</h3>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:24px">Purpose-built feature set for fintechs & neobanks.</p>
<div class="sector-features"><div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Real-Time Scoring API</h4><p>RESTful API with &lt;50ms latency. Score transactions, onboard customers, and flag anomalies instantly.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>KYC Automation</h4><p>Automated identity verification, PEP/sanctions screening, and risk-based onboarding flows.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Device & IP Intelligence</h4><p>Fingerprint devices, detect VPN/proxy/Tor, flag impossible travel, and track session risk.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Fraud Prevention</h4><p>Behavioral anomaly detection, velocity checks, and peer-group comparison for account takeover and payment fraud.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Webhook Integration</h4><p>Push-based event notifications for real-time downstream actions and partner integrations.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>SDK & Developer Tools</h4><p>Python, Java, and Node.js SDKs. OpenAPI spec. Sandbox environment for testing.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sector-panel" id="sector-tax">
<h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px">📋 Tax Authorities</h3>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:24px">Purpose-built feature set for tax authorities.</p>
<div class="sector-features"><div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Invoice Fraud Detection</h4><p>Identify naylon fatura, circular invoicing, and phantom trade through e-invoice and e-waybill analysis.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>E-Invoice Analysis</h4><p>Native support for country-specific electronic invoice formats (GİB, Peppol, EN 16931).</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Trade-Based Laundering</h4><p>Detect over/under invoicing, mismatched shipments, and fictitious goods across trade corridors.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Shell Company Detection</h4><p>Graph-based identification of shell company networks through shared addresses, directors, and patterns.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>VAT Carousel Detection</h4><p>Identify missing trader fraud and carousel schemes across multi-country VAT chains.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Bulk Data Processing</h4><p>Batch analysis of millions of invoices with pattern matching and anomaly scoring.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sector-panel" id="sector-police">
<h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:8px">👮 Financial Police & Law Enforcement</h3>
<p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:24px">Purpose-built feature set for financial police & law enforcement.</p>
<div class="sector-features"><div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Evidence Chain</h4><p>Tamper-proof audit trail with chain of custody for every decision, action, and data access.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Forensic Replay</h4><p>Re-execute historical transactions against point-in-time rules and models for court-ready analysis.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Legal Hold</h4><p>Lock investigation data against deletion or modification during active legal proceedings.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Cross-Case Search</h4><p>Search past investigations for matching entities, patterns, and modus operandi.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>War Room Collaboration</h4><p>Real-time multi-analyst investigation workspace with shared graph and annotation tools.</p></div></div>
<div class="sf-item"><div class="sf-dot"></div><div><h4>Court-Ready Reports</h4><p>Auto-generated investigation summaries with evidence references and chronological narratives.</p></div></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
