<section id="how-it-works">
<div class="container">
<div class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="hw_label">How It Works</div>
<div class="section-title reveal" data-i18n="hw_title">Intelligence at Every Layer.</div>
<div class="section-sub reveal" data-i18n="hw_sub">From raw data to regulatory filing — a fully autonomous pipeline.</div>
<div class="pipeline reveal"><div class="pipe-step" data-step="0">
<div class="pipe-icon">📥</div>
<h4>Data Ingestion</h4>
<p>Batch, streaming, CDC, file upload. Any source, any format.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
<div class="pipe-step" data-step="1">
<div class="pipe-icon">🧠</div>
<h4>AI / ML Engine</h4>
<p>Supervised, unsupervised, and graph neural networks. Continuously learning.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
<div class="pipe-step" data-step="2">
<div class="pipe-icon">🔍</div>
<h4>Pattern Detection</h4>
<p>23+ known patterns plus anomaly detection. Rule engine + ML hybrid.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
<div class="pipe-step" data-step="3">
<div class="pipe-icon">📊</div>
<h4>Risk Scoring</h4>
<p>Multi-layer scoring in &lt;50ms. Transaction, entity, account, network levels.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
<div class="pipe-step" data-step="4">
<div class="pipe-icon">⚖️</div>
<h4>Decision & Action</h4>
<p>Auto-approve, block, or escalate. Configurable approval workflows.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
<div class="pipe-step" data-step="5">
<div class="pipe-icon">📋</div>
<h4>Reporting</h4>
<p>SAR/STR generation, executive dashboards, NLG explanations, audit trails.</p>
<span class="pipe-arrow">→</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="tech-highlights reveal">
<div class="th-card"><h4>Graph Database</h4><p>Neo4j / TigerGraph for billion-edge relationship analysis.</p></div>
<div class="th-card"><h4>Real-Time Streaming</h4><p>Kafka + Flink for sub-second event processing.</p></div>
<div class="th-card"><h4>NLG Explanations</h4><p>LLM-powered natural language narratives for every alert and report.</p></div>
<div class="th-card"><h4>Forensic Replay</h4><p>Re-run any decision against point-in-time rules and models.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<div class="section-divider"></div>

