<section id="architecture">
<div class="container">
<div class="section-label reveal" data-i18n="arch_label">System Architecture</div>
<div class="section-title reveal" data-i18n="arch_title">Built for Scale & Security.</div>
<div class="section-sub reveal" data-i18n="arch_sub">End-to-end platform architecture — from data ingestion to compliance reporting.</div>

<div class="reveal">
<div class="arch-section-label">Data Pipeline</div>
<div class="arch-layer">
<div class="arch-node">
<span class="a-icon">📥</span>
<h4>Data Ingestion</h4>
<p>Kafka, CDC, REST API, SFTP, File Upload</p>
</div>
<span class="arch-arrow">→</span>
<div class="arch-node">
<span class="a-icon">🔗</span>
<h4>Entity Resolution</h4>
<p>Fuzzy matching, identity graphs, golden records</p>
</div>
<span class="arch-arrow">→</span>
<div class="arch-node">
<span class="a-icon">🔍</span>
<h4>Pattern Detection</h4>
<p>Rule engine + ML + graph analytics</p>
</div>
<span class="arch-arrow">→</span>
<div class="arch-node">
<span class="a-icon">📊</span>
<h4>Risk Scoring</h4>
<p>Multi-layer scoring, &lt;50ms real-time</p>
</div>
<span class="arch-arrow">→</span>
<div class="arch-node">
